{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773433579260,"sessionID":"ses_31721ba8fffeXD00hbThRJI7PX","part":{"id":"prt_ce8e0d9d7001gzCNM6bGsG53JI","sessionID":"ses_31721ba8fffeXD00hbThRJI7PX","messageID":"msg_ce8e0cfcd001KDKaApdA6CuLLT","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01K2TSpmbSCwAwhNKe8gJWNp","tool":"bash","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"git add src/index.ts && git commit -m \"feat(toon-format-spec): wire TOON output into describe command\n\nWhen \\`woco describe --output toon\\` is invoked, emit the compact TOON\nlegend (text format) that agents can cache for the session. When a\nspecific command is passed with --output toon, emit its field spec\nas JSON. This makes the spec self-describing: agents learn the format\nwith one call.\"","description":"Commit describe command TOON support"},"output":"[feature/toon-format-spec c542ae9] feat(toon-format-spec): wire TOON output into describe command\n 1 file changed, 32 insertions(+)\n","title":"Commit describe command TOON support","metadata":{"output":"[feature/toon-format-spec c542ae9] feat(toon-format-spec): wire TOON output into describe command\n 1 file changed, 32 insertions(+)\n","exit":0,"description":"Commit describe command TOON support","truncated":false},"time":{"start":1773433579230,"end":1773433579259}}}}
