{"type":"text","timestamp":1773433645634,"sessionID":"ses_31721ba8fffeXD00hbThRJI7PX","part":{"id":"prt_ce8e1bab1001mQJDJmunP4xwbt","sessionID":"ses_31721ba8fffeXD00hbThRJI7PX","messageID":"msg_ce8e1b10b0011FCLNlIrOVK6kn","type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Let me do a final summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\nSuccessfully implemented the TOON (Token-Optimized Output Notation) format specification across 4 files with 4 commits:\n\n### Files changed:\n\n1. **`src/lib/toon-spec.ts`** (new) — The core specification module containing:\n   - **Encode/decode maps** for status codes (BL/PL/IP/BK/IR/DN/CN), priority codes (C/H/M/L/W), and difficulty codes (T/E/M/H/V)\n   - **Duration encoding** — ISO 8601 ↔ compact format (`PT1H30M` ↔ `1h30m`)\n   - **Boolean encoding** — `1`/`0` instead of `true`/`false`\n   - **Null/missing** — empty field between pipes (`||`)\n   - **Array encoding** — comma-separated within a single field\n   - **Per-command field specs** with positional ordering for `tasks list`, `tasks show`, `status`, and `history`\n   - **`buildToonSpec()`** — builds the full structured spec object\n   - **`renderToonLegend()`** — emits a compact text legend for agent consumption\n\n2. **`src/lib/output.ts`** — Extended `OutputFormat` type to `\"text\" | \"json\" | \"toon\"` and updated `resolveOutputFormat()` to recognize `toon` from both `--output` flag and `WOMBO_OUTPUT` env var.\n\n3. **`src/index.ts`** — Wired TOON output into the `describe` command. `woco describe --output toon` emits the compact legend; `woco describe --output toon tasks list` emits the field spec for a specific command.\n\n4. **`src/lib/schema.ts`** — Added `\"toon\"` to the `--output` flag enum in `GLOBAL_FLAGS` so agents can discover it via schema introspection.\n\n### Verification:\n- `bun run typecheck` — passes cleanly\n- `bun run build` — passes (0.93 MB bundle, 151 modules)\n- `bun dev describe --output toon` — outputs the compact, self-describing TOON legend",